---
import BaseLayout from "../layouts/BaseLayout.astro";
---

<BaseLayout title="Help · memoato" description="FAQ and quick start." canonicalPath="/help">
  <section class="section">
    <div class="container prose">
      <h1 class="page-title">Help & FAQ</h1>
      <h2>How do I log something?</h2>
      <p>Open a category and add a number. Adjust date/time when logging past events.</p>
      <h2>Can I edit history?</h2>
      <p>Yes - open a category, scroll history, edit or delete entries.</p>
      <h2>Where do I send feedback?</h2>
      <p>
        For now, email <a href="mailto:hello@memoato.com">hello@memoato.com</a>. A public voting board is planned.
      </p>
      <h2>Do you have privacy options?</h2>
      <p>
        Yes: cloud sync, encrypted cloud, and local-only. Open the app, then go to <strong>Profile → Privacy</strong>.
      </p>
    </div>
  </section>
</BaseLayout>
